📢 Major Update to Desktop App

We are excited to announce a big update to Termius on desktop. The new version makes navigation easier and boosts your productivity with horizontal tabs and the command palette, allowing you to connect and jump between tabs quickly.

*🔐 Keychain moved*

All your data is consolidated under the Vaults tab, including Keychain, which has been moved from settings.

*🎉 Command Palette*

Quickly jump to a tab you need with CMD+J/CTRL+J and a few keystrokes.

*🚀 Rollout plan*

Your desktop app will automatically be updated to the new version later in July. If you want to try it now, download the beta ( https://termius.com/beta-program ).

*📜 Back story*

We shared some of the backstory behind these changes in a recent blog post ( https://www.termius.com/blog/termius-x ).

📈 Import Up to 10,000 Hosts Into Your Vault

Previously, Termius Vault could sync up to *700* hosts at a time. This was sufficient for most of the teams. With larger enterprises switching to Termius, it's time to up our game! What's the new magic number? With the recent update, Termius Vault can sync up to *10,000* hosts in one go.

🙋‍♂️ API Early Access

We are working on the API to sync data from third-party systems into Termius Vault. We will start the rollout with a handful of early adopters. If you are interested in participating, please fill out the form ( https://termius.typeform.com/to/uG7sNMY7#email=emil.skogsund@gmail.com ).

